(31, 1, '2015-02-02 18:24:45', '2015-02-02 23:24:45', '<h3><span style="color: #000000;">To join our team, is to join our family.</span></h3>\r\nOur success depends on the people behind the name. Each individual playing an essential role - often more than one.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1080" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Careers-5.jpg" alt="Love Where You Work." width="660" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1082" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Careers-6.jpg" alt="Creative. Passionate. Motivated. Team Player." width="660" height="50" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-292" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/colleen1.jpg" alt="Colleen Simmons, Account Manager and Designer" width="315" height="220" />We value our employees, encourage their growth, support their strengths and enhance their talent with the latest technology, training and proper tools to facilitate their success. We are continuously looking for experienced and talented team members.\r\n<h3>Inquire today about potential opportunities!</h3>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/colleen1.jpg"> </a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1037" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Careers-2.jpg" alt="Interior Designer, Account Manager, Design Internship, Administration, Installers" width="660" height="150" />\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/colleen1.jpg"> </a>\r\n<h3>Please send all inquiries to:</h3>\r\nJanet Joseph Clayman, President\r\njclayman@champion-industries.com\r\n711 Indiana Avenue, Charleston, WV 25302\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Careers-2.jpg"> </a>', 'Careers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'join-us', '', '', '2015-05-28 10:54:11', '2015-05-28 14:54:11', '', 5, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/about/join-us/', 4, 'page', '', 0),
(32, 1, '2015-02-02 18:25:14', '2015-02-02 23:25:14', '<h2>This phase signifies our developing understanding of your space as it relates to work flow &amp; personal interactions.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1103" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-5.jpg" alt="Programming Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nWorkspaces grow naturally from your organization''s culture. No industry is exactly alike. Our focus is on determining and understanding what that culture is and discovering how we can translate it into spatial terms.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn order to develop personalized design solutions for you, we must know your needs <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>and</em></span> your challenges. From initial consultations, site visits and field measurements, we assess all of your workspace needs.\r\n\r\nYour office should work <em>for you</em>, not against you.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1128" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Programming-1.jpg" alt="Define, Discover, Determine, Distinguish, Develop" width="660" height="250" />', 'Programming', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'programming', '', '', '2015-05-29 11:52:25', '2015-05-29 15:52:25', '', 6, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/expertise/programming/', 5, 'page', '', 0),
(33, 1, '2015-02-02 18:25:14', '2015-02-02 23:25:14', '<h2>This phase signifies the heart of the project.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1104" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-6.jpg" alt="Design Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nUpon gathering in-depth information from our clients, our highly experienced team begins the design phase. We prepare layout options, 3D drawings and renderings, as well as furnishing recommendations and interior finishes to help you visualize your needs from an ideal work environment. Our team works with you to review, explore possibilities and revise your space until you are completely satisfied.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1139" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Design-5.jpg" alt="Design is our passion" width="475" height="297" />Design Services</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Space Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nFinish Selection\r\nRenderings\r\nVisual Presentations\r\nInterior Finishes\r\nSignage Design\r\nAccessories\r\nArtwork</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf a complete renovation is not feasible, our team will work with your existing space and furnishings to determine how to make your space as functional and efficient as possible. From compiling inventory to designing and executing reconfigurations -- we can help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: right;"></h2>', 'Design', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'design', '', '', '2015-05-29 10:51:54', '2015-05-29 14:51:54', '', 6, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/expertise/design/', 6, 'page', '', 0),
(34, 1, '2015-02-02 18:25:14', '2015-02-02 23:25:14', '<h2>This phase signifies our commitment to provide you with solutions to effectively and economically implement your project.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1105" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-7.jpg" alt="Acquisition Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nEstablishing a project budget is critical to success. However, choosing a local dealer who can stay within those parameters is another. Once we have established a direction, we refine all details, project estimates and bidding documents as needed to make your vision a reality.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Quality products. Future assurance.</h2>\r\nEach piece of furniture you buy is an investment in your organization''s future. We specify products that we can stand behind with comprehensive warranty plans.\r\n<h3><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1164" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Acquisition-1.jpg" alt="Budgeting" width="330" height="300" />Partnerships with Manufacturers</h3>\r\nVolume Pricing\r\nSpecial Pricing Agreements\r\nLeasing and Loan Options\r\n<h3>Bid preparation</h3>\r\nClient Liaison\r\nCreate Formal Bid Documents\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Buy Local.</h2>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/connect/">Inquire</a> today for further information.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Acquisition', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'acquisition', '', '', '2015-05-29 11:19:30', '2015-05-29 15:19:30', '', 6, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/expertise/acquisition/', 7, 'page', '', 0),
(35, 1, '2015-02-02 18:25:14', '2015-02-02 23:25:14', '<h2>This phase signifies the integration of services and products.</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1106" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-8.jpg" alt="Installation Phase" width="110" height="100" />Effective installation of your project is the key to making all other facets of the project successful. Your installation is too important to be left to chance. For that reason, Capitol Business Interiors has developed a clearly defined program that consists of a series of techniques and procedures that minimize errors, reduce flaws and enhance the overall aesthetic of the finished project.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Experienced &amp; Trained Installers.<img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1205" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Installation-2.jpg" alt="Installation Crew" width="300" height="300" /></h2>\r\nCapitol Business Interiors is a full-service company. Our skilled installers are certified factory trained experts with years of experience working with virtually every contract manufacturer in the market. From concept to completion -- no detail goes unnoticed.\r\n<h2>Intermarket Program.</h2>\r\nIn addition to the list of services we provide, we are also a valuable resource. Capitol Business Interiors offers an intermarket program to coordinate, manage and install your nationally driven project as needed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Project &amp; Installation Management</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Coordinate with various construction trades\r\nSchedule &amp; organize product delivery with manufacturers\r\nReceive, inspect, stage, deliver and install product\r\nPrepare punch lists of vendor shortages, defects and damages\r\nCommunicate with vendors to get replacements, warranty coverage &amp; service parts</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: medium;"> </span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Installation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'installation', '', '', '2015-05-29 11:01:56', '2015-05-29 15:01:56', '', 6, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/expertise/installation/', 8, 'page', '', 0),
(36, 1, '2015-02-02 18:25:14', '2015-02-02 23:25:14', '<h2>This phase signifies our long-standing commitment to you beyond project completion.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1107" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-9.jpg" alt="Service Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nCapitol Business Interior''s commitment to quality continues through our follow-up services. We offer services that are tailored to your needs in order to maximize the life span of your products.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2>We design with the future in mind.</h2>\r\nIn today''s world, it''s essential to create a flexible work environment that will grow <em>with you</em>, not against you. Often a “facelift” can improve your office environment and at the same time reduce costs and downtime. Capitol Business Interiors works with clients that wish to revise their existing office systems and furniture. When the project needs to be reconfigured, we compare new, used and existing inventory quickly and efficiently to meet your new interior space requirement.\r\n<h2><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1210" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Service-1.jpg" alt="Service Team" width="660" height="300" /></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Post Occupancy Support.</h2>\r\nWhen you have a service request, our account managers and designers are always available for any needs after move-in.\r\n<h3>Service Request</h3>\r\nRepairs\r\nService Part Orders\r\nManufacturer Warranty Claims', 'Service', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'service', '', '', '2015-05-29 11:48:33', '2015-05-29 15:48:33', '', 6, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/expertise/service/', 9, 'page', '', 0),
