(1043, 2, '2015-05-27 17:24:38', '2015-05-27 21:24:38', '<h2>This phase signifies the beginning. The start of a partnership.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1102" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-4.jpg" alt="Contact Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nWe can''t do our job unless we have great clients like yourself to service. If you have an upcoming project, contact us today and let us transform your space. From new and continuing relationships, our experienced design staff and account managers are here to help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>No Limitations.</h2>\r\nNo project is too small. Your needs are our priority. Our commitment is to answer client demands with exceptional service and quality products with integrity, passion and creativity.\r\n<h2>Responsiveness &amp; Reliability.<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Contact-2.jpg"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1125" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Contact-2.jpg" alt="Contact Us" width="238" height="300" /></a></h2>\r\nResponding to your requests in a timely manner is of the utmost importance. Furthermore, following through with our word is imperative. Once paired with one of our experienced account managers, you will have a single point of contact with you throughout the entire process and beyond.\r\n<h2>Comprehensive product offering.</h2>\r\nCapitol Business Interiors has partnered with hundreds of manufacturers in the contract furniture industry allowing us to be your complete, creative, source. We pride ourselves on having a great working relationship with our vendors so our clients can reap the benefits.\r\n\r\nView our <a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/products/">product</a> offerings.', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '742-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 17:24:38', '2015-05-27 21:24:38', '', 742, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/742-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
