(1052, 2, '2015-05-26 18:51:23', '2015-05-26 22:51:23', 'This phase signifies our developing understanding of your space as it relates to work flow &amp; personal interactions.\r\n\r\nWorkspaces grow naturally from your organization''s culture. No industry is exactly alike. Our focus is on determining and understanding what that culture is and discovering how we can translate it into spatial terms.\r\n\r\nIn order to develop personalized design solutions for you, we must know your needs and your challenges.\r\n\r\nFrom initial consultations, site visits &amp; field measurements, we assess all of your workspace needs.\r\n\r\nYour office should work for you, not against you.\r\n\r\nDEFINE overall design direction.\r\nDISCOVER interaction patterns.\r\nDETERMINE hierarchical structures.\r\nDISTINGUISH space planning dilemmas.\r\nDEVELOP a plan of action.', 'Programming', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-26 18:51:23', '2015-05-26 22:51:23', '', 32, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
