(1055, 2, '2015-05-26 18:52:10', '2015-05-26 22:52:10', '<h2>This phase signifies our developing understanding of your space as it relates to work flow &amp; personal interactions.</h2>\r\nWorkspaces grow naturally from your organization''s culture. No industry is exactly alike. Our focus is on determining and understanding what that culture is and discovering how we can translate it into spatial terms.\r\n<h3>In order to develop personalized design solutions for you, we must know your needs <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>and</em></span> your challenges.</h3>\r\nFrom initial consultations, site visits &amp; field measurements, we assess all of your workspace needs.\r\n\r\nYour office should work <em>for you</em>, not against you.\r\n<h2>DEFINE overall design direction.\r\nDISCOVER interaction patterns.\r\nDETERMINE hierarchical structures.\r\nDISTINGUISH space planning dilemmas.\r\nDEVELOP a plan of action.</h2>', 'Programming', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-26 18:52:10', '2015-05-26 22:52:10', '', 32, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1056, 2, '2015-05-27 19:32:38', '2015-05-27 23:32:38', '<h2>This phase signifies the heart of the project.</h2>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-6.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1104" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-6.jpg" alt="Design Phase" width="110" height="100" /></a>\r\n\r\nUpon gathering in-depth information from our clients, our highly experienced team begins the design phase. We prepare layout options, 3D drawings and renderings, as well as furnishing recommendations and interior finishes to help you visualize your needs from an ideal work environment. Our team works with you to review, explore possibilities and revise your space until you are completely satisfied.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1139" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Design-5.jpg" alt="Design is our passion" width="475" height="297" />Design Services</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Space Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nFinish Selection\r\nRenderings\r\nVisual Presentations\r\nInterior Finishes\r\nSignage Design\r\nAccessories\r\nArtwork</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf a complete renovation is not feasible, our team will work with your existing space furnishings to determine and priorities how to make your space as functional and efficient as possible. From compiling inventory to designing and executing reconfigurations; we can help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: right;"></h2>', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 19:32:38', '2015-05-27 23:32:38', '', 33, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/33-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1057, 2, '2015-05-26 20:34:30', '2015-05-27 00:34:30', 'This phase signifies the heart of the project.\r\n\r\nDesign is our passion.\r\n\r\nUpon gathering in-depth information from our clients, our highly experienced team begins the design phase. We prepare layout options, 3D drawings and renderings, as well as furnishing recommendations and interior finishes to help you visualize your needs from an ideal work environment. Our team works with you to review, explore possibilities and revise your space until you are completely satisfied.\r\n\r\nWe innovate, we don''t duplicate.\r\n\r\nIf a complete renovation is not feasible, our team will work with your existing space furnishings to determine and priorities how to make your space as functional and efficient as possible. From compiling inventory to designing and executing reconfigurations; we can help.\r\n\r\nDesign Services\r\n\r\nSpace Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nFinish Selection\r\nRenderings\r\nVisual Presentations\r\nInterior Finishes\r\nSignage Design\r\nAccessories\r\nArtwork', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-26 20:34:30', '2015-05-27 00:34:30', '', 33, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
