(1188, 2, '2015-05-27 20:37:23', '2015-05-28 00:37:23', '<h2>This phase signifies the integration of services and products.</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFurniture is our specialty.\r\n\r\nEffective installation of your project is the key to making all other facets of the project successful. Your installation is too important to be left to chance. For that reason, Capitol Business Interiors has developed a definite program and a series of techniques and procedures that minimize errors, reduce flaws and enhance the overall aesthetic of the finished project.\r\n<h2>Experienced &amp; Trained Installers.</h2>\r\nCapitol Business Interiors is a full-service company. Our skilled installers are certified factory trained experts with years of experience working with virtually every contract manufacturer on the market. From concept to completion; no detail goes unnoticed.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">Project &amp; Installation Management</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Intermarket Program\r\nCoordinate with various construction trades\r\nSchedule &amp; organize product delivery with manufacturers\r\nReceive, inspect, stage, deliver and install product\r\nPrepare punch lists of vendor shortages, defects and damages\r\nCommunicate with vendors to get replacements, warranty coverage &amp; service parts</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Intermarket Program</h2>\r\nIn addition to the list of services we provide, we are also a valuable resource. Capitol Business Interiors offers an intermarket program to coordinate, manage and install your project as needed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Installation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '35-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 20:37:23', '2015-05-28 00:37:23', '', 35, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/35-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
