ation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '35-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 21:49:49', '2015-05-28 01:49:49', '', 35, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/35-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1207, 2, '2015-05-27 21:51:03', '2015-05-28 01:51:03', '<h2>This phase signifies the heart of the project.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1104" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-6.jpg" alt="Design Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nUpon gathering in-depth information from our clients, our highly experienced team begins the design phase. We prepare layout options, 3D drawings and renderings, as well as furnishing recommendations and interior finishes to help you visualize your needs from an ideal work environment. Our team works with you to review, explore possibilities and revise your space until you are completely satisfied.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1139" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Design-5.jpg" alt="Design is our passion" width="475" height="297" />Design Services</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Space Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nFinish Selection\r\nRenderings\r\nVisual Presentations\r\nInterior Finishes\r\nSignage Design\r\nAccessories\r\nArtwork</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf a complete renovation is not feasible, our team will work with your existing space furnishings to determine and priorities how to make your space as functional and efficient as possible. From compiling inventory to designing and executing reconfigurations; we can help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: right;"></h2>', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 21:51:03', '2015-05-28 01:51:03', '', 33, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1208, 2, '2015-05-27 21:51:22', '2015-05-28 01:51:22', '<h2>This phase signifies our developing understanding of your space as it relates to work flow &amp; personal interactions.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1103" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-5.jpg" alt="Programming Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nWorkspaces grow naturally from your organization''s culture. No industry is exactly alike. Our focus is on determining and understanding what that culture is and discovering how we can translate it into spatial terms.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn order to develop personalized design solutions for you, we must know your needs <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>and</em></span> your challenges. From initial consultations, site visits &amp; field measurements, we assess all of your workspace needs.\r\n\r\nYour office should work <em>for you</em>, not against you.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1128" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Programming-1.jpg" alt="Define, Discover, Determine, Distinguish, Develop" width="660" height="250" />', 'Programming', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 21:51:22', '2015-05-28 01:51:22', '', 32, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1209, 2, '2015-05-27 21:53:20', '2015-05-28 01:53:20', '<h2>This phase signifies our long-standing commitment to you beyond project completion.</h2>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-9.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1107" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-9.jpg" alt="Service Phase" width="110" height="100" /></a>\r\n\r\nCapitol Business Interior''s commitment to quality continues through our follow-up services. In today''s world, it''s essential to create a flexible work environment that will grow <em>with you</em>, not against you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>We design with the future in mind.</h2>\r\nOften a “facelift” can improve your office environment and at the same time reduce costs and downtime. Capitol Business Interiors works with clients to create solutions for facilities that wish to revise their existing office systems and furniture. When the project needs to be reconfigured, we compare new, used and existing inventory quickly and efficiently to meet your new interior space requirement.\r\n<h2>Post Occupancy Support.</h2>\r\nWhen you have a service request, our account managers and designers are always available for any needs after move-in.\r\n<h3>Service Request</h3>\r\nRepairs\r\nService part orders\r\nManufacturer Warranty Claims', 'Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 21:53:20', '2015-05-28 01:53:20', '', 36, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
