host:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Roots-12.jpg" alt="Old Capitol Business Logo" width="315" height="220" /></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;">1976</span> | A new logo is created using the letters "CBI" to symbolize the modularity of systems furniture in commercial environments. This also introduced the color red which will become the company''s primary accent color.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1262" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Roots-9.jpg" alt="1960''s Furniture" width="315" height="221" /></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;">1962</span> | Jim Tilson envisions the future of the company and takes the lead by adding interior design as a service.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1264" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Roots-11.jpg" alt="Office Furniture" width="315" height="220" /></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;">1960</span> | Capitol Business Equipment begins shifting the primary focus to office furniture. Capitol Business Interiors is born.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;"><a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Blank-Space.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1278" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Blank-Space.jpg" alt="" width="315" height="220" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;">1958</span> | Capitol Business Equipment is founded by father and son duo, Ben and Jim Tilson as a business equipment and office supply company in Charleston, WV.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;"><a href="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Blank-Space.jpg"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1278" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Blank-Space.jpg" alt="" width="315" height="220" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #cf202e;">1940</span> | Ben Tilson first entered the office supply business in Bluefield, WV.', 'Roots', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-28 16:28:51', '2015-05-28 20:28:51', '', 29, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/29-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
