(1303, 2, '2015-05-28 16:35:45', '2015-05-28 20:35:45', 'Since 1961, Capitol Business Interiors, has built a reputation as the premier interior design firm in the state of West Virginia by creating bold, professional and innovative work environments. As a locally based company, Capitol Business Interiors has two convenient locations in Charleston and Morgantown to serve you in the best way possible.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-974" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/About-2.jpg" alt="People, Service, Quality, Integrity, Passion, Creativity" width="550" height="125" /></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFrom concept to completion, Capitol Business Interiors offers an experienced and qualified staff to help. We are the people who create places for you to congregate, collaborate and conduct business.\r\n<h3><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-946" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/About-1.jpg" alt="We are the people who create places for you to congregate, collaborate and conduct business." width="475" height="297" />Services</h3>\r\nInterior Design\r\nSpace Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nTechnology Integration\r\nFurniture Procurement\r\nProject Management\r\nInstallation\r\nOngoing Support\r\n<h3>Industries</h3>\r\nCorporate\r\nGovernment\r\nEducation\r\nHealthcare\r\nHospitality\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #cf2000;">Capitol Business Interiors + Haworth</span><img class="aligncenter wp-image-948" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Preferred-logo-horiz-blk.jpg" alt="Haworth Preferred Dealer" width="530" height="25" /></span></h1>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-28 16:35:45', '2015-05-28 20:35:45', '', 5, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
