(1364, 2, '2015-05-29 10:39:00', '2015-05-29 14:39:00', 'Since 1961, Capitol Business Interiors has built a reputation as the premier interior design firm in the state of West Virginia by creating bold, professional and innovative work environments. As a locally based company, Capitol Business Interiors has two convenient locations in Charleston and Morgantown to serve you in the best way possible.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-974" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/About-2.jpg" alt="People, Service, Quality, Integrity, Passion, Creativity" width="550" height="125" /></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFrom concept to completion, Capitol Business Interiors offers an experienced and qualified staff to help. We are the people who create places for you to congregate, collaborate and conduct business.\r\n<h3><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-946" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/About-1.jpg" alt="We are the people who create places for you to congregate, collaborate and conduct business." width="475" height="297" />Services</h3>\r\nInterior Design\r\nSpace Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nTechnology Integration\r\nFurniture Procurement\r\nProject Management\r\nInstallation\r\nOngoing Support\r\n<h3>Industries</h3>\r\nCorporate\r\nGovernment\r\nEducation\r\nHealthcare\r\nHospitality\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #cf2000;">Capitol Business Interiors + Haworth</span><img class="aligncenter wp-image-948" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Preferred-logo-horiz-blk.jpg" alt="Haworth Preferred Dealer" width="530" height="25" /></span></h1>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 10:39:00', '2015-05-29 14:39:00', '', 5, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1365, 2, '2015-05-29 10:50:52', '2015-05-29 14:50:52', '<h2>This phase signifies the heart of the project.</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1104" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Expertise-6.jpg" alt="Design Phase" width="110" height="100" />\r\n\r\nUpon gathering in-depth information from our clients, our highly experienced team begins the design phase. We prepare layout options, 3D drawings and renderings, as well as furnishing recommendations and interior finishes to help you visualize your needs from an ideal work environment. Our team works with you to review, explore possibilities and revise your space until you are completely satisfied.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1139" src="http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Design-5.jpg" alt="Design is our passion" width="475" height="297" />Design Services</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Space Planning\r\nProduct Specification\r\nFinish Selection\r\nRenderings\r\nVisual Presentations\r\nInterior Finishes\r\nSignage Design\r\nAccessories\r\nArtwork</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf a complete renovation is not feasible, our team will work with your existing space furnishings to determine and priorities how to make your space as functional and efficient as possible. From compiling inventory to designing and executing reconfigurations -- we can help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: right;"></h2>', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 10:50:52', '2015-05-29 14:50:52', '', 33, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
