(1400, 2, '2015-05-29 12:27:42', '2015-05-29 16:27:42', '<h3>Location:  Charleston, WV</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n"At the outset of the project, we engaged Capitol Business Interiors to design the interior furnishings and finishes of our new Appalachian Headquarters. They worked very closely with our architect and contractor to ensure a cohesive look and feel for the entire building. I found Janet and her staff to be responsive and professional and their services to be reasonable and cost effective. It was a great working experience and we are tremendously pleased with the final results."\r\n\r\n<strong>Ben Sullivan</strong> | Associate General Counsel &amp; Project Manager\r\nEnergy Corporation of America', 'Energy Corporation of America', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '432-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 12:27:42', '2015-05-29 16:27:42', '', 432, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/432-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1401, 2, '2015-05-29 12:28:07', '2015-05-29 16:28:07', '<h3>Location:  Charleston, WV</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n"CBI was crucial to the success of our floor renovations. They brought in clever ideas and delivered quality products on time. Their staff was a pleasure to work with. They provided solutions to fit both our needs and budget. We will trust CBI with any future projects we encounter."\r\n\r\n<strong>Nathan Johnson</strong> | Manager - IT Network Operations\r\nEnerVest LTD', 'EnerVest', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '498-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 12:28:07', '2015-05-29 16:28:07', '', 498, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/498-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1402, 2, '2015-05-29 12:28:29', '2015-05-29 16:28:29', '<h3>Location:  Charleston, WV</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n"Spilman Thomas &amp; Battle, PLLC has partnered with Capitol Business Interiors on several remodeling projects for offices across the firm''s footprint. Most recently, our client waiting area and adjoining conference rooms in Charleston were updated with the help of CBI''s talented staff. The waiting room was a complete redesign of the floor plan and included updating the décor from floor to ceiling. CBI did a great job choosing floor coverings, paint schemes and lighting, initial planning, and working details with the architects. The CBI designers are talented, responsive professionals who are easy to work with and who understand the image we expect to project to our clients and visitors. The designers at CBI did a wonderful job providing us with a specific, unified look for our offices."\r\n\r\n<strong>Jeff Davis</strong> | Facilities Manager\r\nSpilman Thomas &amp; Battle, PLLC', 'Spilman Thomas & Battle, PLLC', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '473-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 12:28:29', '2015-05-29 16:28:29', '', 473, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/473-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
