(1407, 2, '2015-05-29 14:58:30', '2015-05-29 18:58:30', '<h3>Location:  Huntington, WV</h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n"We have worked with CBI on several projects over the years ranging from small Community College classrooms requiring $15,000 in furnishings to a large Applied Engineering Complex with over $1.3 million in furniture and fixtures. Their professionalism in providing the client with quality furnishing, within budget, and on time continues to be a cornerstone of their business. We have also found their assistance in the selecting individual pieces to meet clients functional needs, as well as their design expertise in establishing individual fabric selections or even entire project color schemes has proven invaluable. We continue to look to CBI when design matters."\n\n<strong>John Harris, AIA, NCARB</strong> |\nBastian &amp; Harris, Architects', 'Arthur Weisberg Family Applied Engineering Complex', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '712-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-29 14:58:30', '2015-05-29 18:58:30', '', 712, 'http://localhost:8888/cbiwv/712-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
